\par
L\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh h\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng (Object Oriented Programming \f3\endash  OOP) l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t trong nh\u7919?ng k\u7929? thu\u7853?t l\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh r\f1\lang1066\u7845?t quan tr\u7885?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng nhi\u7873?u hi\u7879?n nay. H\u7847?u h\u7871?t c\f0\lang1033\'e1c ng\'f4n ng\f1\lang1066\u7919? l\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh hi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n nay nh\f2\u432? Java, PHP, .NET, Ruby, Python\'85 \'f0\f1\u7873?u h\u7895? tr\u7907? OOP. V\u7853?y l\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh h\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 g\'ec? V\'e0 c\'e1c nguy\'ean l\'fd c\f2\u417? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n trong OOP c\u7847?n bi\u7871?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 g\'ec?\par
\par
Functional Programming l\'e0 g\'ec?\par
L\f1\lang1066\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh h\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng (OOP) l\f0\lang1033\'e0 g\'ec?\par
L\f1\lang1066\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh h\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng (OOP) l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t k\u7929? thu\u7853?t l\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh cho ph\'e9p l\f1\lang1066\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh vi\'ean t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o ra c\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng trong code tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng h\f0\lang1033\'f3a c\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng.\par
\par
\f2\'d0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng s\u7921? v\u7853?t, s\u7921? vi\u7879?c m\f0\lang1033\'e0 n\'f3 c\'f3 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng t\f0\lang1033\'ednh ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?t, \f2\'f0\f1\u7863?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh, h\'e0nh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng gi\u7889?ng nhau v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ta gom g\'f3p l\f1\lang1066\u7841?i th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng gi\u7889?ng trong th\u7921?c t\u7871? cu\u7897?c s\u7889?ng. Khi l\u7853?p tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh OOP, ch\'fang ta s\f1\lang1066\u7869? \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh ngh\f2\u297?a c\f0\lang1033\'e1c l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p (class) \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? gom (m\f0\lang1033\'f4 h\'ecnh) c\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng th\u7921?c t\u7871?.\par
\par
\f2\'d0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng\par
M\u7897?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng bao g\u7891?m 2 th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin: thu\f1\lang1066\u7897?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh v\'e0 ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c.\par
\par
 Thu\u7897?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh ch\'ednh l\'e0 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin, \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?c \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?m c\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng. V\f0\lang1033\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909?: con ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i c\f0\lang1033\'f3 c\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh nh\f2\u432? m\f1\lang1066\u7855?t, m\f2\u361?i, tay, ch\f0\lang1033\'e2n\'85\par
 Ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng thao t\f0\lang1033\'e1c, h\'e0nh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng m\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 c\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n. V\f0\lang1033\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909?: m\u7897?t ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i s\u7869? c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng n\f0\lang1033\'f3i, \f2\'f0i, \'e3n, u\f1\lang1066\u7889?ng, . . .\par
L\u7899?p\par
M\u7897?t l\u7899?p l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t ki\u7875?u d\u7919? li\u7879?u bao g\u7891?m c\f0\lang1033\'e1c thu\f1\lang1066\u7897?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh v\'e0 c\'e1c ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh ngh\f2\u297?a t\f1\u7915? tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c. \f2\'d0\f0\lang1033\'e2y l\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng h\f0\lang1033\'f3a c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng. Kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i ki\u7875?u d\u7919? li\u7879?u th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng th\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng, m\u7897?t l\u7899?p l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t \f2\'f0\u417?n v\f1\u7883? (tr\u7915?u t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng) bao g\u7891?m s\u7921? k\u7871?t h\u7907?p gi\u7919?a c\f0\lang1033\'e1c ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\'e1c thu\f1\lang1066\u7897?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh. Hi\f1\lang1066\u7875?u n\f0\lang1033\'f4m na h\f2\u417?n l\f0\'e0 c\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng c\f0\lang1033\'f3 c\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh t\f2\u432?\u417?ng t\f1\lang1066\u7921? nhau \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c gom l\u7841?i th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t l\u7899?p \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng.\par
\par
S\u7921? kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c nhau gi\f1\lang1066\u7919?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p\par
L\u7899?p b\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? hi\u7875?u n\f0\lang1033\'f3 nh\f2\u432? l\f0\'e0 khu\'f4n m\f1\lang1066\u7851?u, \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t th\u7921?c th\u7875? th\u7875? hi\u7879?n d\u7921?a tr\f0\lang1033\'ean khu\'f4n m\f1\lang1066\u7851?u \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3. V\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909?: Ta n\f0\lang1033\'f3i v\f1\lang1066\u7873? lo\f0\lang1033\'e0i ch\'f3, b\f1\lang1066\u7841?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? hi\u7875?u n\f0\lang1033\'f3 l\'e0 class (l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p) ch\f0\lang1033\'f3 c\'f3:\par
\par
C\'e1c th\'f4ng tin, \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?c \f2\'f0i\f1\u7875?m: 4 ch\f0\lang1033\'e2n, 2 m\f1\lang1066\u7855?t, c\f0\lang1033\'f3 \f2\'f0u\f0\'f4i, c\'f3 chi\f1\lang1066\u7873?u cao, c\f0\lang1033\'f3 c\'e2n n\f1\lang1066\u7863?ng, m\f0\lang1033\'e0u l\'f4ng\'85\par
C\'e1c h\'e0nh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng nh\f2\u432?: s\f1\u7911?a, \f2\'f0i, \'e3n, ng\f1\u7911?\'85\par
\f2\'d0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng th\f0\lang1033\'ec ch\'ednh l\'e0 con ch\'f3 Ph\'fa Qu\f1\lang1066\u7889?c ta \f2\'f0ang nu\f0\lang1033\'f4i trong nh\'e0 c\f2\u361?ng mang \'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a l\u7899?p ch\f0\lang1033\'f3.\par
