C\'e1c nguy\'ean l\'fd c\f2\u417? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n c\u7911?a OOP\par
T\f0\lang1033\'ednh \f2\'f0\f0\'f3ng g\'f3i (Encapsulation)\par
Note:\par
\par
C\'e1c d\f1\lang1066\u7919? li\u7879?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\f0\lang1033\'f3 li\'ean quan v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i nhau \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3ng g\'f3i th\'e0nh c\'e1c l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? ti\u7879?n cho vi\u7879?c qu\u7843?n l\f0\lang1033\'fd v\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng. T\u7913?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7895?i l\u7899?p \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n m\u7897?t nh\f0\lang1033\'f3m ch\f1\lang1066\u7913?c n\f2\'e3ng \'f0\f1\u7863?c tr\f2\u432?ng c\f1\u7911?a ri\f0\lang1033\'eang l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3.\par
 Ngo\'e0i ra, \f2\'f0\f0\'f3ng g\'f3i c\'f2n \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? che gi\u7845?u m\u7897?t s\u7889? th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin v\'e0 chi ti\f1\lang1066\u7871?t c\f0\lang1033\'e0i \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7863?t n\u7897?i b\u7897? \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? b\f0\lang1033\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng th\f1\lang1066\u7875? nh\f0\lang1033\'ecn th\f1\lang1066\u7845?y.\par
C\f0\lang1033\'e1c thu\f1\lang1066\u7897?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh v\'e0 ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng c\u7847?n cho vi\u7879?c gi\u7843?i quy\u7871?t b\f0\lang1033\'e0i to\'e1n \f2\'f0\f0\'e3 \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c ch\u7885?n ra s\u7869? \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3ng g\'f3i v\'e0o m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t ki\u7875?u d\u7919? li\u7879?u g\u7885?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0 class. Nh\f1\lang1066\u7857?m che d\u7845?u th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng tin kh\f1\lang1066\u7887?i c\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng b\f0\lang1033\'ean ngo\'e0i, thu\f1\lang1066\u7897?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh n\'e0o th\'ec ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c n\u7845?y. T\u7913?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0 code b\'ean ngo\'e0i kh\'f4ng tr\f1\lang1066\u7921?c ti\u7871?p nh\f0\lang1033\'ecn th\f1\lang1066\u7845?y v\f0\lang1033\'e0 thay \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7893?i tr\u7841?ng th\f0\lang1033\'e1i c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3.\par
