OOP-Encapsulation\par
N\f0\lang1033\'f3i chung tr\f1\lang1066\u7841?ng th\f0\lang1033\'e1i \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng h\f1\lang1066\u7907?p l\u7879? th\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng do: ch\f2\u432?a \'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c ki\u7875?m tra t\f0\lang1033\'ednh h\f1\lang1066\u7907?p l\u7879?, c\f0\lang1033\'e1c b\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng \f2\'f0\f0\'fang tr\'ecnh t\f1\lang1066\u7921? ho\u7863?c b\u7883? b\u7887? qua n\f0\lang1033\'ean trong OOP c\'f3 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t quy t\u7855?c quan tr\u7885?ng c\u7847?n nh\u7899? \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 l\'e0 ph\f1\lang1066\u7843?i lu\f0\lang1033\'f4n khai b\'e1o c\'e1c tr\f1\lang1066\u7841?ng th\f0\lang1033\'e1i b\'ean trong c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a \f2\'f0\f1\u7889?i t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng l\f0\lang1033\'e0 private v\'e0 ch\f1\lang1066\u7881? cho truy c\u7853?p qua c\f0\lang1033\'e1c public/protected method/property.\par
\par
V\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909? ta th\u7845?y m\u7897?t vi\f0\lang1033\'ean thu\f1\lang1066\u7889?c ch\u7919?a c\u7843?m. Ch\f0\lang1033\'fang ta ch\f1\lang1066\u7881? bi\u7871?t n\f0\lang1033\'f3 ch\f1\lang1066\u7919?a c\u7843?m s\u7893? m\f2\u361?i nh\f1\u7913?c \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t s\u7889? th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh ph\f1\lang1066\u7847?n ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh, c\'f2n c\f1\lang1066\u7909? th\u7875? b\f0\lang1033\'ean trong n\'f3 c\'f3 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng ho\u7841?t ch\u7845?t g\f0\lang1033\'ec th\'ec ho\'e0n to\'e0n kh\'f4ng bi\f1\lang1066\u7871?t.\par
\par
T\f0\lang1033\'ednh k\f1\lang1066\u7871? th\u7915?a (Inheritance)\par
N\f0\lang1033\'f3 cho ph\'e9p x\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng m\u7897?t l\u7899?p m\u7899?i d\u7921?a tr\f0\lang1033\'ean c\'e1c \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7883?nh ngh\f2\u297?a c\f1\u7911?a l\u7899?p \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 c\'f3. C\'f3 ngh\f2\u297?a l\f0\'e0 l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p cha c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? chia s\u7869? d\u7919? li\u7879?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\f2\u432?\u417?ng th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c cho c\f0\lang1033\'e1c l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p con. C\f0\lang1033\'e1c l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p con kh\u7887?i ph\u7843?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh ngh\f2\u297?a l\f1\u7841?i, ngo\f0\lang1033\'e0i ra c\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? m\u7903? r\u7897?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e1c th\'e0nh ph\f1\lang1066\u7847?n k\u7871? th\u7915?a v\f0\lang1033\'e0 b\f1\lang1066\u7893? sung th\f0\lang1033\'eam c\'e1c th\'e0nh ph\f1\lang1066\u7847?n m\u7899?i. T\f0\lang1033\'e1i s\f1\lang1066\u7917? d\u7909?ng m\f0\lang1033\'e3 ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n 1 c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch t\f1\lang1066\u7889?i \f2\u432?u, t\f1\u7853?n d\u7909?ng \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c m\f0\lang1033\'e3 ngu\f1\lang1066\u7891?n. M\u7897?t s\u7889? lo\u7841?i k\u7871? lo\u7841?i k\u7871? th\u7915?a th\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?ng g\u7863?p: \f2\'f0\u417?n k\f1\u7871? th\u7915?a, \f2\'f0a k\f1\u7871? th\u7915?a, k\u7871? th\u7915?a \f2\'f0a c\f1\u7845?p, k\u7871? th\u7915?a th\u7913? b\u7853?c.\par
\par
Khi b\u7855?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng \u7913?ng d\u7909?ng ch\f0\lang1033\'fang ta s\f1\lang1066\u7869? b\u7855?t \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?u thi\u7871?t k\u7871? \f2\'f0\f1\u7883?nh ngh\f2\u297?a c\f0\lang1033\'e1c l\f1\lang1066\u7899?p tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c. Th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng th\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7901?ng m\u7897?t s\u7889? l\u7899?p c\f0\lang1033\'f3 quan h\f1\lang1066\u7879? v\u7899?i nh\u7919?ng l\u7899?p kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c, ch\'fang c\'f3 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7863?c t\f0\lang1033\'ednh gi\f1\lang1066\u7889?ng nhau.\par
